        <ul>
          <li>CLI utility that parses logs at <b>1–2 GB/s</b> on a single core.</li>
          <li>Auto-detects: JSON, Syslog (RFC 3164), Nginx/Apache Combined, KV.</li>
          <li>Emits NDJSON — pipe into <code>jq</code>, grep, or anything downstream.</li>
